item.dc:creator: @killerman93 killerman93
item.description:
@killerman93 wrote:

[quote=“goatee, post:2, topic:135650”]6/10

By blurring the stock it has made your sig bland and without a focal point. You need to make the colours less monotone and the empty space above her back is … wasted. The text is badly placed.

Put “Mojo Muhammed” close to her head then put “Keira Knightly” (which you spelt wrong in your sig) like 2 pixels underneath and a little to the left.

Also change the font and size to whatever looks good.

One question; Why does it look like it has streaky lines across it as if you lightly smudged it with a line?

Other than that its not an utter disaster, it’s just a bit boring.[/quote]

I blurred on purpose, because im really bad at rendering.
